{"type": "article", "id": 16362, "title": "隐藏耳机的吊坠", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-21T06:58:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135544sOEPNwQ6xS0q72Kf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t很多设计帮助解决耳机线缠绕影响美观的问题。这款项链隐藏了一对耳机，打开下面的吊坠物，就能将耳机的听筒取出来戴在耳朵上。脖子后用来连接三根链条的部分也是一个插孔，使用时拔下来就能直接插在手机的孔上。吊坠是用不锈钢和铝打造的，可以选择 24K 镀金或青铜与银搭配的颜色组合。对那些经常使用耳机办公或热爱煲电话粥的女生是非常实用的。<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-dipper-audio-necklace-by-tinsel#/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143647z28WKayweLoGqisC.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143647kxSTbW7ygE0lUIVw.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"498\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143648t906d8CPaz5gm2XB.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"392\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143648q6FJXAtWpYBED0eL.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"505\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143649CVwsLokOxqA48bit.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}